snippet.title: Ni no Kuni: Cross Worlds Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Ni no Kuni: Cross Worlds is now available for download! Experience new adventures in the world of Ni no Kuni. Choose one of five playable classes and begin the journey of a lifetime. Dive into your new fantasy world! https://ntiny.link/ninokunicw1
